returned his token to the inn?

285
00:17:12,839 --> 00:17:13,519
Exactly.

286
00:17:13,519 --> 00:17:14,880
So 43 years ago,

287
00:17:14,880 --> 00:17:16,119
Luan Yi did not die

288
00:17:16,119 --> 00:17:17,200
or disappear.

289
00:17:17,200 --> 00:17:19,599
