than the chain and base.

456
00:22:31,200 --> 00:22:32,599
After combining them,

457
00:22:34,039 --> 00:22:35,119
how can it not be suspicious?

458
00:22:36,839 --> 00:22:37,400
Sir.

459
00:22:37,400 --> 00:22:38,200
Sir.

460
00:22:38,480 --> 00:22:39,400
