00:27:15,119 --> 00:27:16,079
About five or six.

568
00:27:16,559 --> 00:27:17,359
All can fight.

569
00:27:17,559 --> 00:27:18,480
How old are they?

570
00:27:18,759 --> 00:27:20,359
They are all young,

571
00:27:20,359 --> 00:27:21,720
in their early twenties.

572
00:27:23,000 --> 00:27:24,400
Waiter, serve the wine.

573
00:27:24,680 --> 00:27:25,400
Alright.

574
00:27:54,200 --> 00:27:54,920
After you, please.

575
00:28:02,119 --> 00:28:03,519
How dare you spoil my mood.

576
00:28:04,880 --> 00:28:06,440
You're so useless.

577
00:28:07,456 --> 00:28:07,968
Sir.

578
00:28:07,968 --> 00:28:08,480
Get lost.

579
00:28:09,559 --> 00:28:10,799
What do you think you are?

580
00:28:11,240 --> 00:28:12,119
How dare you stop me.

581
00:28:13,000 --> 00:28:13,720
I'm telling you.

582
00:28:14,119 --> 00:28:15,880
I won't pay you.

583
00:28:16,319 --> 00:28:16,920
What can you do?

584
00:28:23,000 --> 00:28:23,559
What?

585
00:28:24,400 --> 00:28:26,039
You wanna fight?

586
00:28:27,240 --> 00:28:27,759
Come on.

587
00:28:42,240 --> 00:28:44,359
This terrible place

588
00:28:44,759 --> 00:28:46,559
spoiled my mood.

589
00:28:59,119 --> 00:29:00,000
It's alright.

590
00:29:00,519 --> 00:29:02,039
Don't let this ruin your mood.

591
00:29:02,519 --> 00:29:04,119
Lin.

592
00:29:04,680 --> 00:29:05,559
Sweep the floor.

593
00:29:07,000 --> 00:29:08,039
Sorry, guys.

594
00:30:23,599 --> 00:30:24,799
It's been 43 years.

595
00:30:25,039 --> 00:30:26,240
Your kung fu is still good.

596
00:30:32,839 --> 00:30:35,279
Have you been hiding
in a brothel for 43 years?

597
00:30:55,617 --> 00:30:57,312
(Luan Yi's Token)

598
00:30:57,440 --> 00:30:59,119
Anyway, you are my senior.

599
00:30:59,599 --> 00:31:00,559
Let's drink together.

600
00:31:10,480 --> 00:31:11,720
The dishes here are sweet.

601
00:31:12,240 --> 00:31:13,039
Are you used to it?

602
00:31:14,000 --> 00:31:15,480
It's been 43 years.

603
00:31:16,720 --> 00:31:17,799
I have to adapt to it.

604
00:31:18,440 --> 00:31:19,599
Take this shrimp.

605
00:31:20,519 --> 00:31:22,400
I couldn't even peel it before.

606
00:31:23,319 --> 00:31:25,200
Now, after I finish the shrimp,

607
00:31:27,880 --> 00:31:29,319
I can put the shell back together.

608
00:31:32,400 --> 00:31:33,519
In this place,

609
00:31:34,240 --> 00:31:36,359
the cook puts the fresh shrimp
directly in the pot

610
00:31:37,000 --> 00:31:38,359
and blanches it with seawater.

611
00:31:39,160 --> 00:31:40,519
Do not add any seasoning.

612
00:31:42,640 --> 00:31:44,359
If you live here for ten years,

613
00:31:44,680 --> 00:31:45,799
you will grow to like it.

614
00:31:54,976 --> 00:31:57,632
(Luan Yi's Token)

615
00:32:10,839 --> 00:32:11,440
Yes.

616
00:32:12,960 --> 00:32:14,079
43 years ago,

617
00:32:16,200 --> 00:32:17,759
I indeed served as the Emperor's guard.

618
00:32:18,799 --> 00:32:22,240
I came here to do a job
for the imperial yamen.

619
00:32:25,480 --> 00:32:26,680
But I am not Luan Yi.

620
00:32:28,000 --> 00:32:29,240
I am Luan Yi's deputy.

621
00:32:31,319 --> 00:32:32,759
What kind of person is Luan Yi?

622
00:32:33,559 --> 00:32:34,839
He was a first-class imperial guard,

623
00:32:35,759 --> 00:32:36,920
a senior third-rank official.

624
00:32:36,920 --> 00:32:38,079
His kung fu was superb.

625
00:32:38,720 --> 00:32:42,680
He was extremely loyal to the court.

626
00:32:43,960 --> 00:32:45,720
However, he was extremely violent.

627
00:32:46,440 --> 00:32:47,279
In 1868,

628
00:32:47,279 --> 00:32:49,519
you were ordered to come here
to investigate the Altar Treasure.

629
00:32:50,079 --> 00:32:51,599
It was Luan Yi who led the team, right?

630
00:32:52,559 --> 00:32:54,599
What did you find back then?

631
00:33:01,079 --> 00:33:01,920
We found something,

632
00:33:04,880 --> 00:33:05,759
or we didn't.

633
00:33:07,079 --> 00:33:08,480
It's been 43 years.

634
00:33:11,000 --> 00:33:12,319
Some people have left.

635
00:33:13,799 --> 00:33:15,319
And those who should die have all died.

636
00:33:16,680 --> 00:33:18,039
There's nothing to hide.

637
00:33:20,599 --> 00:33:21,799
I can tell you everything.

638
00:33:25,200 --> 00:33:26,240
In 1868,

639
00:33:27,599 --> 00:33:28,920
my mission

640
00:33:30,599 --> 00:33:32,400
was to find the Altar Treasure.

641
00:33:33,279 --> 00:33:34,920
But we found nothing.

642
00:33:36,759 --> 00:33:38,160
Southern Shaolin was gone,

643
00:33:38,519 --> 00:33:40,880
and we didn't know
if their descendants were still alive.

644
00:33:40,880 --> 00:33:41,880
Even if they were alive,

645
00:33:42,960 --> 00:33:44,400
we didn't know where they were.

646
00:33:45,440 --> 00:33:46,839
So in that area,

647
00:33:47,640 --> 00:33:50,160
we began a cruel search.

648
00:33:51,440 --> 00:33:52,880
I say so

649
00:33:53,720 --> 00:33:55,519
because Luan Yi's investigative methods

650
00:33:56,000 --> 00:33:57,599
were utterly inhumane.

651
00:33:58,200 --> 00:33:59,480
He always believed

652
00:34:00,079 --> 00:34:02,039
that a Xianghua monk
who appeared in Fujian

653
00:34:02,519 --> 00:34:05,160
had an inseparable connection
with Southern Shaolin.

654
00:34:07,000 --> 00:34:09,239
(That Xianghua monk once appeared)

655
00:34:09,360 --> 00:34:10,800
(at the locals' weddings and funerals.)

656
00:34:11,679 --> 00:34:12,559
(In that case,)

657
00:34:13,199 --> 00:34:16,199
(Luan Yi violently
elicited confessions.)

658
00:34:26,119 --> 00:34:27,440
You're a funeral director.

659
00:34:27,440 --> 00:34:28,639
Don't you know the Xianghua monk?

660
00:34:29,199 --> 00:34:30,480
Say no again,

661
00:34:30,679 --> 00:34:31,760
and I will kill you.

662
00:34:36,719 --> 00:34:37,639
I hear

663
00:34:38,159 --> 00:34:40,239
a Xianghua monk is invited
to your wedding.

664
00:34:40,800 --> 00:34:42,039
You find them.

665
00:34:42,880 --> 00:34:45,840
Otherwise,
I'll send you more bridegrooms.

666
00:34:51,119 --> 00:34:53,920
The Xianghua monk Luan Yi tried to find
was called Wu Shuangbao.

667
00:34:54,840 --> 00:34:55,840
Finally, one day,

668
00:34:56,360 --> 00:34:58,480
he found Wu Shuangbao staying

669
00:34:59,280 --> 00:35:00,599
at the Futu Temple in the east.

670
00:35:01,320 --> 00:35:02,119
So,

671
00:35:04,480 --> 00:35:05,760
he led his men to kill him.

672
00:35:08,760 --> 00:35:09,440
However,

673
00:35:11,440 --> 00:35:13,119
something strange happened.

674
00:35:14,679 --> 00:35:15,719
On the way

675
00:35:15,719 --> 00:35:17,480
to the Futu Temple,

676
00:35:17,639 --> 00:35:19,079
we contracted malaria.

677
00:35:19,599 --> 00:35:21,079
Some of us died on the road.

678
00:35:21,639 --> 00:35:24,920
The remaining ones, including Luan Yi,

679
00:35:26,760 --> 00:35:28,519
were all on the brink of death.

680
00:35:34,159 --> 00:35:35,320
(We arrived)

681
00:35:35,920 --> 00:35:37,920
(at the Futu Temple like ghosts,)

682
00:35:39,320 --> 00:35:41,840
(completely without the bravery
of the imperial guards.)

683
00:35:42,440 --> 00:35:44,519
(Each of us was dying.)

684
00:35:46,199 --> 00:35:47,559
(And the one who saved us)

685
00:35:47,920 --> 00:35:49,599
(was the very Xianghua monk)

686
00:35:50,000 --> 00:35:52,119
(we were looking for.)

687
00:36:00,480 --> 00:36:02,559
(Wu Shuangbao
and the abbot of the Futu Temple)

688
00:36:02,800 --> 00:36:04,800
(saved our lives.)

689
00:36:08,960 --> 00:36:10,280
(After escaping death,)

690
00:36:10,920 --> 00:36:12,280
(everyone was moved.)

691
00:36:13,000 --> 00:36:14,199
(We thanked Wu Shuangbao)

692
00:36:15,280 --> 00:36:18,679
(and decided to give up catching him.)

693
00:36:29,800 --> 00:36:32,039
(However, Luan Yi did not allow it.)

694
00:36:33,760 --> 00:36:36,079
(When the other guards refused
to carry out the orders,)

695
00:36:37,159 --> 00:36:38,800
Luan Yi acted as if possessed
by a demon,

696
00:36:41,840 --> 00:36:44,760
killing his subordinates.

697
00:36:48,079 --> 00:36:49,480
(When Wu Shuangbao arrived,)

698
00:36:50,000 --> 00:36:51,360
(the bodies were all over the ground.)

699
00:36:51,920 --> 00:36:54,280
(Luan Yi was going on a killing spree.)

700
00:36:56,320 --> 00:36:57,719
Do you also disobey?

701
00:36:57,719 --> 00:36:58,400
Sir.

702
00:36:58,400 --> 00:36:59,599
He saved our lives.

703
00:37:37,119 --> 00:37:38,519
This is the line.

704
00:37:46,079 --> 00:37:47,199
If you cross this line,

705
00:37:48,519 --> 00:37:49,719
I will kill you.

706
00:38:14,079 --> 00:38:16,280
I said if you cross this line,
I will kill you.

707
00:38:20,416 --> 00:38:25,472
(Futu Temple)

708
00:38:42,754 --> 00:38:46,370
♪Blood refines the sword,
and wind forges the blade♪

709
